    "description": {
      "value": "<p>A bioelectrically-charged battery, capacitor, and shock pad are embedded in the hand, activating in contact with an opponent. When the user grapples an enemy, the enemy automatically takes 1d6 damage directly to their HP at the start of the user's turn. If an electrified grip is installed in 2 or more hands that are being used to grapple, this damage is changed to a flat 7 instead. This damage does not interact with armor, and if an enemy is incapacitated by it, is considered non-lethal.</p><p>Can be installed as the only piece of cyberware in a meat arm.</p>"
